    Nighteyes screamed as several of the bullets dug into her armor, and then 
fell back to cover behinde the log. Angry, she poked up and tossed a plasam 
grenade at Starscream.

    Black Aracnia looked at her mate. "What do you mean? You cant leave 
me...like this. Our daughter is gone. And...and were on the verge of another 
victory. Please Quicky...dont go."
    Then something occured to her that really pissed Black Aracnia off. "And 
who the hell is this other person damn it? Are you ceating on me, because  
iswaer by the Pit if you are I will cut off every protruding organ you have!"
